  <h1>You might be independent, but you're not alone.</h1>
  <p>Join Cowork Niagara today and qualify for a three-day trial pass so that you can see for yourself how joining Niagara's coworking community can improve your earnings by up to 30%.</p>
  <p><a href="/join.html">Sign up for my three-day trial.</a></p>
  <p>Still unsure? No problem; we get it. We put the most common questions below, so feel free to explore and sign up when you're ready.</p>
  <ul class="questions">
    <li>
      <h2>Is coworking a good fit for me?</h2>
      <p>Are you a freelancer? Solopreneur? Micro-Enterprise? Single-person small business? Professional practice?</p>
      <p>All these terms describe members of the independent workforce, and if you connect with any of these
      (or even one we haven't heard of yet), then it might be a good fit.</p>
      <p>Either way, you won't really know until you get started. So come out to some events and some of our
      free sessions to see if it's a good fit before you join.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h2>Does this sound like it fits? Find out for sure with a free three-day trial pass.</h2>
      <p>We know that if you spend three days with us, you'll know everything you need to know to make your decision.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>
